(246,70,"top_left_copy","Almar tooling is a company that specializes in custom CNC tool creation. A core part of their business is the ability for their customers to submit custom tooling requests that generates a PDF of the tool and its specifications. So when this functionality broke, it was paramount that it got fixed. "),
