(252,70,"bottom_right_copy","We had moved the site to an upgraded server running PHP 7, however, this particular site is somewhat old and that move caused key functionality to break. The solution? Move back to a PHP 5 environment. This fixed some issues but the custom tooling functionality was still down. After scouring the error logs I was able to determine the fault was coming from PHPmailer. We had to configure PHPmailer, and WPsmtp, and we were finally able to get the custom tooling functionality back online. "),
