(274,79,"top_left_copy","My Student Village/ My Campus Living is a company that helps students find housing for universities across the globe. My work for them consists of change requests, building pop-ups, minor edits, and content updates. Some more exciting work has been investigative and required digging deep into the files, and error logs to uncover the issue. Specifically, we had what seemed like a simple change request to update a button link. However, no matter what we did the link would not change and kept updating to a strange URL when pushed live. We suspected that something malicious was going on... Eventually, we discovered that Google Tag Manager was to blame for changing the URL after we had updated it on our end. "),
