(331,31,"top_left_copy","Edison energy came to Gravitate with a request to increase the number of icons they could use on their map on the contact page of their site. This was in an effort to emphasize the fact that they are a global energy producer. The map originally just showed the companies US locations. Zooming out the map was easy enough however we encountered several problems when the map was zoomed out. "),
