(337,31,"bottom_right_copy","The map was clustering all the points in the US when zoomed out so that it appeared only one location was visible in the US. I ended up tapping into the API and re-configuring our call to it to un-cluster icons when zoomed out. The client was quite happy with the result and felt it met their goals of improving the emphasis on their global position in the energy business. "),
